collectionMetadata.name: Public Transport Journeys - Average Distance Per Trip
collectionMetadata.description: Passenger journeys based on public transport mode (MRT, LRT and public buses).

datasetMetadata.name: Public Transport Journeys
datasetMetadata.description:
Data on Journeys is average over the period from January - December.

A journey refers to as a series of consecutive trips on different modes (MRT, LRT, bus), made by a commuter from his origin to his destination.
